    {
      "id": "PopularPost353800",
      "post_content": "I run this guy in a WG heroic centric deck and it's great. The ordeals are really fun on this guy yes, but my 2 favorite cards to put on this are [Gift of Orzhova](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gift of Orzhova) (flyinng+lifelink ftw) and  [Murder Investigation](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Murder Investigation) (Sure he's really big, but if you kill him, I'm going to swarm you to death).  \n  \nThe Murder Investigation choice is especially fun because I also run [Phalanx Leader](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phalanx Leader), and his heroic just gets better and better the more creatures you get.",
      "posted_by": "Orichalcum",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost353800\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">I run this guy in a WG heroic centric deck and it's great. The ordeals are really fun on this guy yes, but my 2 favorite cards to put on this are <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Gift of Orzhova\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gift of Orzhova\">Gift of Orzhova</a> (flyinng+lifelink ftw) and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\" Murder Investigation\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Murder Investigation\"> Murder Investigation</a> (Sure he's really big, but if you kill him, I'm going to swarm you to death).<br/><br/>The Murder Investigation choice is especially fun because I also run <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Phalanx Leader\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phalanx Leader\">Phalanx Leader</a>, and his heroic just gets better and better the more creatures you get.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '353800'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy81767\">Orichalcum</span>\r\n                                (12/7/2013 12:07:23 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n        